Invocation Name: say yes
des:
Do you want to say yes, but you're not sure how? Use this skill to have Alexa say yes for you!

This skill will step in and say "yes" any time you need it to. If you are tired of being negative and turning down people's requests, this skill is for you! Try it out!

To use, simply say, "Alexa open Say Yes!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
